\c 5
\s Kupindura kwechikomba
\p
\v 1 Ndapinda mubindu rangu, hanzvadzi yangu, mwenga; ndatanha mura yangu nezvinonhuhwira zvangu; ndadya zinga reuchi hwangu pamwe neuchi hwangu; ndanwa waini yangu pamwe nemukaka wangu. Idyai, shamwari dzangu; inwai, zvirokwazvo inwai zvikuru, vadiwa.
\p
\v 2 Ndakarara, asi moyo wangu wakamuka, inzwi remudiwa wangu rinogogodza \add richiti\add*: Ndizarurire, hanzvadzi yangu, shamwari yangu, njiva yangu, wakakwana wangu; nokuti musoro wangu uzere dova, mhotsi dzangu nemadonhedza eusiku.
\v 3 Ndabvisa nguvo refu yangu; ndingaipfeka sei? Ndashambidza tsoka dzangu; ndingadzisvibisa sei?
\v 4 Mudiwa wangu wakapinza ruoko rwake nepaburi \add regonhi\add*, zvino ura hwangu ndokufamba mandiri.
\v 5 Ini ndakasimuka kuzarurira mudiwa wangu; uye maoko angu akadonha mura*, neminwe yangu mura inoyerera, pazvibato zvekiyi.
\v 6 Ini ndakazarurira mudiwa wangu; asi mudiwa wangu wakange atendeuka akapfuura. Mweya wangu wakabuda paakataura, ndakamutsvaka asi handina kumuwana, ndakamudana asi haana kundipa mhinduro.
\v 7 Varindi vanofamba-famba neguta vakandiwana; vakandirova, vakandikuvadza; vachengeti vemasvingo vakasimudza kwiriti yangu kubva pandiri.
\v 8 Ndinokupikisai, imwi vakunda veJerusarema, kana mukawana mudiwa wangu, muchamuudzei? Kuti ndinorwarwa rudo.
\p
\v 9 Mudiwa wako anopfuura \add vamwe\add* vadiwa nei, iwe, wakanaka pakati pevakadzi? Mudiwa wako anopfuura nei \add umwe\add* mudiwa zvaunotipikisa saizvozvo?
\p
\v 10 Mudiwa wangu wakachena uye mutsvuku, anozikanwa pakati pemazana gumi.
\v 11 Musoro wake igoridhe rakaisvonaka; mhotsi dzake mapazi, itema segunguvo.
\v 12 Meso ake akaita senjiva pahova dzemvura, dzakashambidzwa mumukaka, dzakarongedzwa zvakanaka.
\v 13 Matama ake akaita sendima yemiti inonhuhwira, \add se\add*matutu zvifafaidzo zvinobudisa mweya unonhuhwira. Miromo yake mafurauzi anodonha mura.
\v 14 Maoko ake akaita sepombi dzegoridhe dzine bheriri*; dumbu rake inyanga yenzou inoonekwa, yakafukidzwa nesafiro*.
\v 15 Makumbo ake imbiru dzemabwe machena, dzakateiwa pazvigadziko zvegoridhe rakaisvonaka; kuonekwa kwake kwakaita seRebhanoni, rakasanangurwa semisidhari.
